after a number of conversations

00:01:52.350 --> 00:01:55.920 align:middle line:84%
and emails and Skype calls
between the UK and India,

00:01:55.920 --> 00:01:59.610 align:middle line:84%
we decided to set off to India
in the hope of seeing more

00:01:59.610 --> 00:02:02.690 align:middle line:90%
for ourselves.

00:02:02.690 --> 00:02:06.380 align:middle line:84%
