with a very low standard

00:02:46.130 --> 00:02:49.010 align:middle line:84%
of living compared
to Western countries.

00:02:49.010 --> 00:02:51.470 align:middle line:84%
And most people
work many more hours

00:02:51.470 --> 00:02:54.950 align:middle line:84%
and earn far less in a month
than even the lowest paid

00:02:54.950 --> 00:02:57.658 align:middle line:84%
hourly worker in the
