to my native place, which is

00:03:51.710 --> 00:03:55.610 align:middle line:10%
called Bobbili, in rural India.

00:03:55.610 --> 00:03:59.630 align:middle line:10%
This is in the
southeast of India,

00:03:59.630 --> 00:04:03.290 align:middle line:10%
and it is rather a
very, very poor place.

00:04:03.290 --> 00:04:07.750 align:middle line:10%
This is the place where
I was started my clinic.

00:04:07.750 --> 00:04:08.870 align:middle line:90%
This is my house.

00:04:08.870 --> 00:04:10.010 align:middle line:90%
That's my clinic.

00:04:10.010 --> 00:04:12.500 align:middle line:84%
>> Although India is considered
one of the fastest growing

00:04:12.500 --> 00:04:15.150 align:middle line:84%
countries in the
technological age,

00:04:15.150 --> 00:04:18.050 align:middle line:84%
there are still many villages
without both electricity

00:04:18.050 --> 00:04:21.829 align:middle line:84%
