as if time has stood still.

00:04:29.480 --> 00:04:31.670 align:middle line:84%
In this village here,
the majority of people

00:04:31.670 --> 00:04:35.150 align:middle line:84%
make their living as farmers or
by chopping and gathering wood

00:04:35.150 --> 00:04:37.740 align:middle line:90%
from the nearby forests to sell.

00:04:37.740 --> 00:04:41.010 align:middle line:84%
So it is ironic that in
this place, where people

00:04:41.010 --> 00:04:44.130 align:middle line:84%
are so steeped in the traditions
of the past and change

00:04:44.130 --> 00:04:46.800 align:middle line:84%
comes so slowly,
that a development

00:04:46.800 --> 00:04:49.620 align:middle line:84%
in medical treatment that
has the potential of changing

00:04:49.620 --> 00:04:53.380 align:middle line:84%
millions of lives
was first discovered.

00:04:53.380 --> 00:04:57.590 align:middle line:10%
>> I'm very happy that
I have got my own house.

00:04:57.590 --> 00:05:01.690 align:middle line:10%
This is 150-year-old small
house that is not even five feet

00:05:01.690 --> 00:05:05.590 align:middle line:10%
width area, in which I
put some tables and chairs

00:05:05.590 --> 00:05:08.300 align:middle line:10%
and then started my
practice, that's how.

00:05:08.300 --> 00:05:09.740 align:middle line:10%
I didn't have any beds.

00:05:09.740 --> 00:05:12.980 align:middle line:10%
I am only a prescribing
doctor doing

00:05:12.980 --> 00:05:15.480 align:middle line:10%
injections, small,
small treatments,

00:05:15.480 --> 00:05:17.880 align:middle line:10%
