much of an acquaintance

00:05:55.490 --> 00:05:58.835 align:middle line:10%
with my patients rather
than not with patients.

00:05:58.835 --> 00:06:01.000 align:middle line:10%
They are my soulmates.

00:06:01.000 --> 00:06:04.431 align:middle line:10%
So things are going
very gradually.

00:06:04.431 --> 00:06:08.720 align:middle line:10%
I have very successful
treating fevers, diarrheas,

00:06:08.720 --> 00:06:12.110 align:middle line:10%
and successful in
conducting deliveries.

00:06:12.110 --> 00:06:15.930 align:middle line:10%
At the time, people used to
pose me a question-- doctor,

00:06:15.930 --> 00:06:19.400 align:middle line:10%
can't you do something
to our joint pains?

00:06:19.400 --> 00:06:20.855 align:middle line:10%
I said, well, why not?

00:06:20.855 --> 00:06:25.710 align:middle line:10%
When I write ibuprofen or an
aspirin or something like that,

00:06:25.710 --> 00:06:28.250 align:middle line:10%
the failure was at my end.

00:06:28.250 --> 00:06:30.020 align:middle line:10%
So I went into a
deep introspection.

00:06:30.020 --> 00:06:33.630 align:middle line:10%
I thought of, I can't alleviate
these joint pains on a subject,

00:06:33.630 --> 00:06:34.560 align:middle line:10%
I have learnt.

00:06:34.560 --> 00:06:36.110 align:middle line:10%
So I went into
deep introspection

00:06:36.110 --> 00:06:39.150 align:middle line:10%
and starting pursuing
for various things.

00:06:39.150 --> 00:06:42.440 align:middle line:10%
So at that time,
except the textbook,

00:06:42.440 --> 00:06:45.380 align:middle line:10%
there is no other
area to learn things.

00:06:45.380 --> 00:06:49.140 align:middle line:10%
Now one of the commonest ways
to get the medical information

00:06:49.140 --> 00:06:52.070 align:middle line:10%
is the medical reps,
medical representatives.

00:06:52.070 --> 00:06:54.260 align:middle line:10%
They used to bring the
information from the company

00:06:54.260 --> 00:06:56.190 align:middle line:10%
to our doorstep.

00:06:56.190 --> 00:06:58.520 align:middle line:10%
So I got what all
the information we

00:06:58.520 --> 00:07:01.560 align:middle line:10%
do judiciously, the practice.

00:07:01.560 --> 00:07:05.450 align:middle line:10%
So one fine morning one fellow
introduced a medicine which

00:07:05.450 --> 00:07:08.270 align:middle line:10%
actually works for allergies.

00:07:08.270 --> 00:07:12.890 align:middle line:10%
So then next time, I'm
having a very rich number

00:07:12.890 --> 00:07:17.430 align:middle line:10%
of patients, patients that
was not a problem to me.

00:07:17.430 --> 00:07:20.840 align:middle line:10%
So obviously, when I give them
this medicine, their allergy,

00:07:20.840 --> 00:07:23.510 align:middle line:10%
like skin allergy and
an asthmatic wheeze,

00:07:23.510 --> 00:07:25.810 align:middle line:10%
these things starts coming down.

00:07:25.810 --> 00:07:28.070 align:middle line:10%
So I was happy,
and they are happy.

00:07:28.070 --> 00:07:30.120 align:middle line:10%
Suddenly one fine
morning, one fellow

00:07:30.120 --> 00:07:36.890 align:middle line:10%
said, sir, I used to suffer
from so many pains and also

00:07:36.890 --> 00:07:38.540 align:middle line:10%
the asthmatic wheeze.

00:07:38.540 --> 00:07:42.150 align:middle line:10%
With your medication, I
am happy for my wheeze

00:07:42.150 --> 00:07:44.320 align:middle line:10%
as I am for my joint pains.

00:07:44.320 --> 00:07:46.370 align:middle line:10%
I am puzzled up.

00:07:46.370 --> 00:07:48.200 align:middle line:10%
The very next moment,
another fellow

00:07:48.200 --> 00:07:49.570 align:middle line:10%
came with the joint pains.

00:07:49.570 --> 00:07:54.950 align:middle line:10%
He used tons and tons
of so many antibiotics,

00:07:54.950 --> 00:07:58.700 align:middle line:10%
so many painkillers,
and including steroids.

00:07:58.700 --> 00:08:02.450 align:middle line:10%
At the time, his face is
swollen, legs are swollen,

00:08:02.450 --> 00:08:05.510 align:middle line:10%
and his condition
is so pathetic.

00:08:05.510 --> 00:08:08.730 align:middle line:10%
So since I have the information
that, yeah, that fellow is all

00:08:08.730 --> 00:08:12.525 align:middle line:10%
right, I simply say,
why can't I try this?

00:08:12.525 --> 00:08:15.090 align:middle line:10%
So I try this medicine.

00:08:15.090 --> 00:08:16.820 align:middle line:10%
This is really
miraculous to work.

00:08:16.820 --> 00:08:18.740 align:middle line:10%
This fellow is happy.

00:08:18.740 --> 00:08:20.910 align:middle line:10%
Within no time, in a
couple of one or two days,

00:08:20.910 --> 00:08:23.090 align:middle line:10%
he comes back and
said, doctor, I'm

00:08:23.090 --> 00:08:25.320 align:middle line:10%
so happy with your medicine.

00:08:25.320 --> 00:08:28.190 align:middle line:10%
So then one by one, joint
pain people used to come,

00:08:28.190 --> 00:08:31.600 align:middle line:10%
and I use it to give
the same kind of regime,

00:08:31.600 --> 00:08:34.570 align:middle line:10%
what I have given
to this fellow.

00:08:34.570 --> 00:08:37.070 align:middle line:10%
Suddenly, my curation
rate is better.

00:08:37.070 --> 00:08:41.289 align:middle line:10%
