to the arthritis.

00:08:43.845 --> 00:08:48.740 align:middle line:10%
Of course, it is only a common
name given by the community.

00:08:48.740 --> 00:08:52.760 align:middle line:10%
I was not enjoy
any joy out of it,

00:08:52.760 --> 00:08:56.220 align:middle line:10%
but I am keen in observing
all these things.

00:08:56.220 --> 00:09:00.320 align:middle line:10%
When one fellow is
suffering from joint pains

00:09:00.320 --> 00:09:05.990 align:middle line:10%
