sequel, he came to me and said,

00:09:05.990 --> 00:09:08.210 align:middle line:10%
doctor, along with
my joint pains,

00:09:08.210 --> 00:09:11.180 align:middle line:10%
the paralysis is also better.

00:09:11.180 --> 00:09:12.960 align:middle line:10%
I was confused.

00:09:12.960 --> 00:09:15.695 align:middle line:10%


00:09:15.695 --> 00:09:18.090 align:middle line:10%
After that, I have
decided that I

00:09:18.090 --> 00:09:22.476 align:middle line:10%
have to understand the
basic science behind it.

00:09:22.476 --> 00:09:28.470 align:middle line:10%
I have given the message
to the very important

00:09:28.470 --> 00:09:31.530 align:middle line:10%
medical specialists
in this country,

00:09:31.530 --> 00:09:33.870 align:middle line:10%
and they have responded to me.

00:09:33.870 --> 00:09:37.510 align:middle line:10%
After that, I have
realized that I

00:09:37.510 --> 00:09:41.670 align:middle line:10%
am meddling with some
important portion

00:09:41.670 --> 00:09:44.850 align:middle line:10%
in the field of immunology.

00:09:44.850 --> 00:09:48.245 align:middle line:10%
Immunology is not a
developed science yet.

00:09:48.245 --> 00:09:50.340 align:middle line:84%
And as a rural
doctor, I don't know

00:09:50.340 --> 00:09:53.050 align:middle line:90%
what is meant by immunology.

00:09:53.050 --> 00:09:55.420 align:middle line:10%
So I've decided to study it.

00:09:55.420 --> 00:10:01.320 align:middle line:10%
For the study, I have sacrificed
my practice, a little practice

00:10:01.320 --> 00:10:06.300 align:middle line:10%
I started in '84 and left for
the education after a decade.

00:10:06.300 --> 00:10:11.110 align:middle line:10%
So in 1993, I have joined
in MD-microbiology.

00:10:11.110 --> 00:10:12.860 align:middle line:10%
Why I took specifically
microbiology

00:10:12.860 --> 00:10:16.190 align:middle line:10%
is, microbiology is the science
which contains immunology.

00:10:16.190 --> 00:10:19.950 align:middle line:84%
So then offered myself for
another more higher study.

00:10:19.950 --> 00:10:23.040 align:middle line:84%
I went to All Indian Institute
for Medical Sciences.

00:10:23.040 --> 00:10:26.640 align:middle line:10%
I could get an opportunity
to do immunology there.

00:10:26.640 --> 00:10:29.370 align:middle line:10%
There I had all
the modern science

00:10:29.370 --> 00:10:32.820 align:middle line:10%
and conducted my
animal experiments.

00:10:32.820 --> 00:10:34.770 align:middle line:10%
And in this process,
I could come

00:10:34.770 --> 00:10:37.740 align:middle line:10%
to know all these
days I am arresting is

00:10:37.740 --> 00:10:40.840 align:middle line:10%
nothing but inflammation.

00:10:40.840 --> 00:10:43.440 align:middle line:10%
So the inflammation is the crux.

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:44.770 align:middle line:90%
So I was surprised.

00:10:44.770 --> 00:10:47.820 align:middle line:84%
I had good success
that I found out

00:10:47.820 --> 00:10:51.440 align:middle line:84%
that the product what I am using
is arresting the inflammation.

00:10:51.440 --> 00:10:58.320 align:middle line:10%
Inflammation is the body's
natural defense process.

00:10:58.320 --> 00:11:00.660 align:middle line:10%
This is like a
cooking fire, which

00:11:00.660 --> 00:11:03.810 align:middle line:10%
is, as long as it is
useful for us to cook,

00:11:03.810 --> 00:11:05.270 align:middle line:10%
fire is a very good thing.

00:11:05.270 --> 00:11:08.410 align:middle line:10%
And fire suddenly, it flames,
burns the entire house.

00:11:08.410 --> 00:11:10.110 align:middle line:10%
But the fire is fire.

00:11:10.110 --> 00:11:13.350 align:middle line:10%
So the inflammation is
the protecting fire.

00:11:13.350 --> 00:11:17.910 align:middle line:10%
It comes, flares up, arrests
the thing, and protects us.

00:11:17.910 --> 00:11:21.120 align:middle line:10%
This is the game
that nature has given

00:11:21.120 --> 00:11:25.240 align:middle line:10%
to all the biological species.

00:11:25.240 --> 00:11:28.120 align:middle line:10%
So in the inflammation,
there are so many layers.

00:11:28.120 --> 00:11:30.390 align:middle line:10%
So finally,
inflammation is always

00:11:30.390 --> 00:11:33.720 align:middle line:10%
interlinked with the
process called healing.

00:11:33.720 --> 00:11:37.510 align:middle line:10%
Inflammation and healing,
they go hand in hand.

00:11:37.510 --> 00:11:40.740 align:middle line:10%
So the inflammation is
due to any reason delayed,

00:11:40.740 --> 00:11:42.460 align:middle line:10%
the healing is delayed.

00:11:42.460 --> 00:11:46.660 align:middle line:10%
And if healing is delayed,
the illness is delayed.

00:11:46.660 --> 00:11:50.530 align:middle line:10%
So at the time, I have
studied further and further

00:11:50.530 --> 00:11:52.530 align:middle line:10%
